{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304400,"lipSynch":1,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3044_00_01","textHome":"我是PROMISED BLOOD的一员，@智珠兰华。嘛，带着一些目的，最近转学到@了神滨。下次带我去游戏厅吧。然后，一起@玩格斗游戏吧？打招呼的时候会顺便好好疼@爱你的。…因为你是，神滨的魔法少女对吧@？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304400,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304400,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":304400,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":304400,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304400}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":7.35,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304400,"lipSynch":1,"motion":300,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3044_00_17","textHome":"虽然还是会有尴尬的时候…但是感觉我和青之@间…有了合适的距离感…。前几天也一起去@了游戏中心，一起玩了…"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.9,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":304400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":304400,"motion":0}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.25,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304400,"lipSynch":1,"motion":200,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3044_00_18","textHome":"虽然有着强大的力量，但却只会往前冲的树里@，和擅长制定攻略的我很合得来吧。只是我@们都是性格强硬的人，经常吵架算是美中不@足吧"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"id":304400,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":304400,"motion":300}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":304400,"lipSynch":1,"motion":100,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3044_00_19","textHome":"噢！大招好像解锁了哦！快去试一下吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304400,"motion":0}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":304400,"lipSynch":1,"motion":1,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3044_00_20","textHome":"我们的现在可是建立在牺牲之上的，绝不能浪@费"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":304400}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304400,"lipSynch":1,"motion":300,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3044_00_21","textHome":"以前，我觉得必须服从强者才能活下去。但是@，现在不同了。就算是强大的家伙也无所谓@。让我不爽的话我就会把他揍飞！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":304400,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":304400,"motion":200}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":304400,"lipSynch":1,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3044_00_22","textHome":"和树里的相遇改变了我。树里向即使变成了魔@法少女，也只能服从有力量的人的我伸出了@援手，教会了我抗争的方法…。所以从今往@后，我也会一直追随着树里"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":304400,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.3,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":304400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":304400,"motion":0}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":8.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304400,"lipSynch":1,"motion":300,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3044_00_23","textHome":"在我承受不住妈妈的压力，快要崩溃的时候，@是游戏给了我容身之处和勇气。所以我想要@保护那个重要的地方是理所当然的吧！为此@而成为魔法少女我没有一丝犹豫"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":304400,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":304400,"motion":0}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304400,"lipSynch":1,"motion":300,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3044_00_24","textHome":"嗯唔，你意外的挺闲的啊？啊哈哈，不要那么@认真的拒绝啊。来嘛，陪我一起吧。我又不@会去干坏事"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":304400,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304400,"motion":1}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.22,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304400,"lipSynch":1,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3044_00_25","textHome":"早上好。没想到你还挺早起的？我该说是擅长@还是已经变成习惯了呢。在这件事上，我妈@从以前就很啰嗦啊"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304400,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":304400}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":8.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304400,"lipSynch":1,"motion":300,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3044_00_26","textHome":"啊～~…已经不行了。肚子快要饿死了～…！@要不要去买点什么呢…不，不行不行！这里@必须要自己做饭节约才行…"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":304400,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304400,"motion":0,"tear":1}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":304400,"lipSynch":1,"motion":1,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3044_00_02","textHome":"…我是智珠兰华。…怎么说呢，好久没用过本@名了。在网上用的也是网名。啊，那个可不@会告诉你哦。好友申请什么的太烦人了"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.05,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.05,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":304400,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304400,"motion":200}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304400,"lipSynch":1,"motion":1,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3044_00_27","textHome":"高中生放学之后去打工吗…。哈啊，我也想早@点去打工啊。…啊，打工的地点游戏中心就@好了。就算在打工也可以随便玩！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":304400,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":304400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":304400,"motion":100}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.55,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":304400,"lipSynch":1,"motion":400,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3044_00_28","textHome":"糟了!?已经这个时间了啊！再不快点登上网@游的话！活动已经开始了，身为公会会长的@我不在的话可是不行的！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.95,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304400,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":304400,"motion":200}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":304400,"lipSynch":1,"motion":200,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3044_00_29","textHome":"快去做作业什么的烦死了！那个老早就完成了@！啊，已经没有动力了。去游戏里切换一下@头脑吧"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304400,"motion":300}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":304400,"lipSynch":1,"motion":300,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3044_00_30","textHome":"好了，该去巡逻了。还没有准备好吗？那就等@你10秒吧。10・9・8…所以说！不要@磨磨蹭蹭的啊！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304400,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":304400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":304400,"motion":200}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":304400,"lipSynch":1,"motion":1,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3044_00_31","textHome":"诶？有一个能完全复制魔法少女的可怕场所啊@…。真是，神滨有太多异常的事情了，什么@都有可能的感觉啊"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.01,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":304400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304400,"motion":300}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304400,"lipSynch":1,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3044_00_32","textHome":"像这样敌人和伙伴们混杂在一起的大乱斗，感@觉就像是赌上性命的游戏一样让人兴奋…！@好，就让你们见识一下，身为玩家的骨气吧@！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.01,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":304400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":304400,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.6,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":304400,"motion":1}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":304400,"lipSynch":1,"motion":200,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3044_00_33","textHome":"啊，不行不行！完全没掌握刹车啊！想要攻克@这个弯道对吧!?再跑一遍，给我把车的性@能都装进脑袋里！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":304400,"motion":1}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304400,"lipSynch":1,"motion":1,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3044_00_34","textHome":"虽然我经常被邀请参加网游的线下网友见面会@，但是我还没去过。只要凭借着网名和聊天@的内容想象一下会是什么样的人就满足了"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304400,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.01,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":304400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304400}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":304400,"lipSynch":1,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3044_00_35","textHome":"我啊，之前在老家的游戏中心里修行的时候，@顺便把音游的分数都刷新了一遍。然后我就@在那附近变得出名了呢"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":304400,"motion":100}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304400,"lipSynch":1,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3044_00_36","textHome":"这个给你。刚才在起重机游戏里抓到的玩偶。@我对奖品没什么兴趣，只是喜欢抓到那时候@的成就感。…回礼什么的不需要啊"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":9.9,"chara":[{"id":304400,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":304400,"motion":400}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304400,"lipSynch":1,"motion":300,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3044_00_03","textHome":"你是无法击败我的，还没搞明白吗？"}]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":8.6,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":